snippet.title: TripleJump Itch.io Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy the game here: https://rebrand.ly/triple-jump-game

Triple Jump is an auto-running puzzle platformer where you have a library of different “jumps” that you can assign in any combination to three slots.  You are then faced with levels that require some combination of those jumps to solve.

This trailer features music from:
Tallbeard Studios - https://tallbeard.itch.io/three-red-hearts-prepare-to-dev
JDBArtist - https://jdbartist.itch.io/retro-music-pack

Additional credits can be found here:
https://rebrand.ly/triple-jump-credits

Closed captioning for title cards:
0:46 - Shidaro is that you?
0:56 - Will you ever see this?
1:09 - I've created a simulation for you to learn from.
1:26 - I've always loved jumping games with special abilities.
1:35 - I've made this one a little more cerebral to help lure you into consciousness.
1:46 - Confronted with the alternative, I will not give up on my sanity, which means... I need this to work.
2:07 - I can't get you out of my mind... perhaps this can help bring us both some peace.

TripleJump and all related original materials are
Copyright 2021, Lee Saenz
